	"keywords": "Software Development, versioning, Dependency Management, Deployment",
	"description": "Releasing modern software might seem daunting and complicated. In this article,\nI&#x27;ll expand on the concepts involved in the process, from managing dependencies\nto building in the cloud.\n\nArticles and tutorials usually cover a specific tool and dive right into it\nbefore laying down the foundational knowledge. In this article, I&#x27;ll provide\nthat foundation by introducing the concepts that go into these tools.\n\nThe topics I&#x27;ll cover include dependency management (and what dependencies\nreally are!), ",
	"headline": "Release Management for Modern Software Development – How to Manage Dependencies, SemVer, and Build Systems for Beginners",
