	"keywords": "Self Improvement, Communication, Collaboration, Productivity",
	"description": "Knowing how to ask effective technical questions is an essential skill every\nsoftware engineer should have. \n\nYou may be stuck with a bug, unable to figure out why your program isn&#x27;t working\ncorrectly, or you might be having trouble learning how to implement a certain\nalgorithm.\n\nIn all of these situations (and more) you&#x27;ll most likely go online and post a\nquestion on Stack Overflow, some community on Discord, a subreddit, a Facebook\ngroup, or even just send it to a friend. \n\nThese tips will equ",
